Created attachment 25713
Icon from oxygen icon set, that kills the transcoder.

The attachted icon can not be transcoded from SVG to PNG. A TranscoderException: null occurs. W3C says that the Icon is valid SVG 1.0 (with missing DOCTYPE). Other icons can be transcoded.
creator: gerasch@informatik.uni-tuebingen.de
